OL,6,FSt Saviour Constable Kevin Lewis
OL,7,Fconfirmed a "significant explosion
OL,8,Foccurred near the Merton Hotel in St
OL,9,FSaviour" and called it a "critical
OL,10,Fincident".
OL,12,FA major incident had been declared but
OL,13,Fthis has now been stood down as they
OL,14,Fmove to the recovery phase.
OL,16,FEmergency services including 20
OL,17,Ffirefighters were called to an
OL,18,Funexplained explosion at a property in
OL,19,FLe Mont Pinel in St Saviour around
OL,20,F11pm on Wednesday night (26 June).
