OL,6,FThey found a house with significant
OL,7,Fdamage that was structurally unsafe.
OL,9,FTwo adults were trapped underneath
OL,10,Frubble and rescued, along with two
OL,11,Fyoung children.
OL,13,FJersey Fire and Rescue Station
OL,14,FCommander Ryan Hall explains: "This
OL,15,Fwas a difficult extraction due to the
OL,16,Fdamage to the building and there were
OL,17,Fconcerns that it may collapse at any
OL,18,Ftime.
