OL,6,F"This was a challenging situation for
OL,7,Femergency services, and I thank them
OL,8,Ffor their quick thinking and bravery."
OL,10,FJersey's Chief Minister, Deputy Lyndon
OL,11,FFarnham, says: "We commend them for
OL,12,Ftheir quick thinking and actions in
OL,13,Fsaving the lives of the family who, in
OL,14,Fthe case of the two adults, were under
OL,15,Frubble.
