OL,6,F"The fact that two young children were
OL,7,Fremoved from the upstairs of the
OL,8,Fproperty unharmed, when there were
OL,9,Fconcerns that the building could
OL,10,Fcollapse, is exceptional. The island
OL,11,Fis incredibly grateful."
OL,13,FA total of 19 residents were evacuated
OL,14,Ffrom their homes as a precaution and
OL,15,Fmoved into temporary accommodation.
OL,17,FDeputy Farnham adds: "Our thoughts are
OL,18,Fwith the family affected and those who
OL,19,Fhave been displaced as a result. The
OL,20,FGovernment is providing ongoing
OL,21,Fsupport to those families.
