OL,6,FOne resident who lives 20 metres away
OL,7,Ffrom the house did not want to be
OL,8,Fnamed but says: "I was lying in bed
OL,9,Fand it sounded like someone had driven
OL,10,Finto the side of my bedroom. The bang
OL,11,Fis like something I can't even
OL,12,Fdescribe.
OL,14,F"When I came out, I could just hear
OL,15,Fsomeone saying, 'Call an ambulance and
OL,16,Fthe fire brigade' so I phoned them.
OL,17,FThen I looked up and saw all the wall
OL,18,Fwas blown out.
OL,20,F"I just felt sick, I could see the
OL,21,Fbunkbeds."
