OL,6,FAnother neighbour, Karen Basile, adds:
OL,7,F"I was sitting on my bed and there was
OL,8,Fan enormous bang which shook the whole
OL,9,Fhouse, it woke everybody up.
OL,11,F"The fire service moved everybody back
OL,12,Fand within seconds of them clearing
OL,13,Fthat area, more of the house fell.
OL,15,F"At one point I heard the person in
OL,16,Fcharge say, 'I want everybody out
OL,17,Falive' so it was obviously a very
OL,18,Fdangerous situation."
