OL,6,FThe surrounding area is closed to the
OL,7,Fpublic as the States of Jersey Police
OL,8,Fremain on the scene with a cordon in
OL,9,Fplace until the evening of Monday 1
OL,10,FJuly but school traffic is not
OL,11,Fexpected to be affected and Mont
OL,12,FMillais is open.
OL,14,FThe cause of the explosion is
OL,15,Fcurrently unknown.
OL,17,FIsland Energy, the mains gas supplier,
OL,18,Fand Jersey Electricity also attended.
