OL,6,FAn Island Energy spokesperson says:
OL,7,F"Within the areas we were allowed to
OL,8,Fsurvey there was no gas escape
OL,9,Fdetected on the evening of the
OL,10,Fincident and our teams returned last
OL,11,Fnight to ensure that the area is safe
OL,12,Fand secure.
OL,14,F"We continue to receive zero readings
OL,15,Fof gas in the area. Island Energy has
OL,16,Fnot conducted any work in this area in
OL,17,Fthe last two years and we want to
OL,18,Freassure people that we have conducted
OL,19,Fall the relevant safety checks."
